#             with documented Zig FFI migration path to `%foreign "C:burble_resample,libburblemedia"`.
#             Commit bf0eef3 pushed to GitHub.
# 2026-04-16: Phase 0 scrub-baseline — deleted api/v/ (V-lang client), api/zig/ (broken
